  "detailed_description": "Welcome to Mage's Legacy, where you will be immersed in a magical world full of mystery and excitement! In this game, players will take on the role of a talented mage, using special magic skills and controlling powerful beasts.<br>Your mission is to bravely fight fierce monsters, collect valuable items to complete difficult missions. Each level will take you into different challenges, from mysterious caves to dark forests, where many secrets are waiting to be discovered.<br>To confront the strongest boss, you need to collect all three mystical gems. Only when you have them, can you enter the lord's territory and face this great challenge. Use smart tactics and combine your magic skills to win!<br><br><strong>GAME FEATURES:</strong><br><strong>Normal Attack:</strong> The player will attack the monster with a magical sword<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139690/extras/46f299a2be07ba1247e26ca8a00cd41e.poster.avif?t=1723707750\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139690/extras/46f299a2be07ba1247e26ca8a00cd41e.webm?t=1723707750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139690/extras/46f299a2be07ba1247e26ca8a00cd41e.mp4?t=1723707750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Special Skill:</strong> The player will attack the monster with any type of skill equipped by the player<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139690/extras/16e982def6d613ab2c2e9ef2114b5717.poster.avif?t=1723707750\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139690/extras/16e982def6d613ab2c2e9ef2114b5717.webm?t=1723707750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139690/extras/16e982def6d613ab2c2e9ef2114b5717.mp4?t=1723707750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Spirit Beast:</strong> A type of pet that will assist the player in battle<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139690/extras/ecd037687da3ab8b2f16b5ffdf6ba0dc.poster.avif?t=1723707750\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139690/extras/ecd037687da3ab8b2f16b5ffdf6ba0dc.webm?t=1723707750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139690/extras/ecd037687da3ab8b2f16b5ffdf6ba0dc.mp4?t=1723707750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Welcome to Mage's Legacy, where you will be immersed in a magical world full of mystery and excitement! In this game, players will take on the role of a talented mage, using special magic skills and controlling powerful beasts.<br>Your mission is to bravely fight fierce monsters, collect valuable items to complete difficult missions. Each level will take you into different challenges, from mysterious caves to dark forests, where many secrets are waiting to be discovered.<br>To confront the strongest boss, you need to collect all three mystical gems. Only when you have them, can you enter the lord's territory and face this great challenge. Use smart tactics and combine your magic skills to win!<br><br><strong>GAME FEATURES:</strong><br><strong>Normal Attack:</strong> The player will attack the monster with a magical sword<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139690/extras/46f299a2be07ba1247e26ca8a00cd41e.poster.avif?t=1723707750\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139690/extras/46f299a2be07ba1247e26ca8a00cd41e.webm?t=1723707750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139690/extras/46f299a2be07ba1247e26ca8a00cd41e.mp4?t=1723707750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Special Skill:</strong> The player will attack the monster with any type of skill equipped by the player<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139690/extras/16e982def6d613ab2c2e9ef2114b5717.poster.avif?t=1723707750\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139690/extras/16e982def6d613ab2c2e9ef2114b5717.webm?t=17237077